name: Louisiana Wings
description: A classic pub appetizer with medium-heat.
preparation: Toss wings with seasoning. Place on Sheet Pan lined with Sheet Pan Liner. Bake for 25–30 min, or until cooked through.
tips: Prefer saucy wings? In a bowl, whisk 1 tbsp each Louisiana Wing Seasoning, ketchup, water, and 1⁄4 cup vinegar. Toss cooked wings in prepared sauce.
